HEADWORD: Anilic
<hw>An*il"ic</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or obtained from, anil; indigotic; -- applied to an
acid formed by the action of nitric acid on indigo.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
